                <p class="text-gray-800 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">U ovoj vježbi ćete naučiti o streptomicetima i njihovim antibiotskim svojstvima. Vježba obuhvaća:</p>
                
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm mb-6">
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">Sadržaj vježbe:</h4>
                  <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium mr-3">1</span>
                      <span>Izolacija streptomiceta iz tla na Czapekovom agaru</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                      <span class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm font-medium mr-3">2</span>
